IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://iondistrict.com/wp-
 content/uploads/2026/06/HLUG_Crest.png
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://iondistrict.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06
 /HLUG_Crest.png
UID:RLdTfhaFkHeRNFKGYVY8N
SUMMARY:Houston Linux User Group
DTSTAMP:20260618T044225Z
DTSTART:20260618T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you interested or already invested in the Linux Operating S
	ystem?\nJoin us at the Houston Linux User Group\, one of the oldest user g
	roups involved with the Linux Operating System. We discuss new trends in o
	perating system usage\, software development\, and current technological t
	rends\, as well as provide one-on-one training or class-based instruction.
	 Learn about how to get more out of your computer or how to leverage any o
	f the Linux-based computational platforms.\nAll are welcome to attend\, re
	gardless of whether you’re a seasoned Linux professional intent on network
	ing or a new Linux user struggling with installation or the command line.\
	nThis monthly meeting includes all of the standard Houston Linux User Grou
	p meeting activities\, which include meet-and-greet\, presentations of per
	sonal projects\, multi-meeting classes\, as well as organizational and coo
	rdinating announcements. \nVisit our website at: https://www.houstonlinux.
	org/\nVisit our calendar and the agenda of each week’s meeting at: https:/
	/calendar.google.com/calendar/u/0/embed?src=houstonlinuxusergroup@gmail.co
	m \nJoin us on social media.\nDiscord: https://discord.gg/MPzYfeJz\nReddit
	: https://www.reddit.com/r/houstonlinuxusergroup/\n\nhttps://iondistrict.c
	om/event/houston-linux-user-group-5/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/houston-linux-user-group-5/
LOCATION:Ion – Conference Room 029 – 030\, 4201 Main St\, Houston\, TX\, 77
	002\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ion-district
CATEGORIES:Ion District
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://houstonarboretum.o
 rg/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Katie-with-Katydid.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://houstonarboretum.org/wp-content/uploads/2
 025/04/Katie-with-Katydid.jpg
UID:0dVBOjwxPE85dN5MP-YsR
SUMMARY:Summer Camp All Grown Up
DTSTAMP:20260618T044225Z
DTSTART:20260618T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Why should kids have all the fun? Treat yourself to all the joy
	s of summer camp\, but for grown-ups! Unwind after a stressful day with ha
	nds-on nature activities\, crafts\, and outdoor exploration\, PLUS a simpl
	e snack and a refreshing beer from Saint Arnold Brewing Company. \n\n\n\nP
	lease dress for the weather and wear walking shoes. \n\n\n\n$22 member / $
	37 nonmember per classThursday\, June 18 and July 16Ages 21+ \n\n\n\n\n\n\
	n\nMicro World\n\n\n\nThursday\, June 18 \n\n\n\nThere’s a whole world of 
	activity going on under our noses. Using hand lenses and microscopes\, we’
	ll hunt for the tiny creatures that make our ecosystems function\, from ro
	ly-polies to plankton. We’ll even create a miniature world to take home: a
	 micro-terrarium! \n\n\n\n\nregister online\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCSI Nature\n\
	n\n\nThursday\, July 16 \n\n\n\nNature is full of mysteries\, and you can 
	find clues everywhere if you know what to look for. Learn about signs of w
	ildlife activity like tracks and scat\, make your own gourmet chocolate “s
	cat snacks\,” and search the trails for evidence of the Arboretum’s “usual
	 suspects.” \n\n\n\n\nregister online\n\nhttps://houstonarboretum.org/even
	t/summer-camp-all-grown-up/2026-06-18/\n\nFrom Houston Arboretum & Nature 
	Center
URL:https://houstonarboretum.org/event/summer-camp-all-grown-up/2026-06-18/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-arboretum
CATEGORIES:Houston Arboretum & Nature Center
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
