	t the Box Office. Box Office opens 1 hour prior to door times. You will ne
	ed a valid photo ID and the credit card used for purchase. Accessible tick
	ets can be purchased online - you do not need to call the box office to pl
	ace an order. Look for the logo on the Find Tickets page to view all avail
	able accessible seats. We do have accessible seating in every price range 
