BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://hermannpark.org/wp
 -content/uploads/2026/06/Red-White-Cruise-2026.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://hermannpark.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/0
 6/Red-White-Cruise-2026.jpg
UID:Fg7EAKZ39ezRd8HywNwSc
SUMMARY:Red\, White & Cruise
DTSTAMP:20260618T044225Z
DTSTART:20260704T203000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Red\, White & Cruise where you can watch Miller Out
	door Theatre’s fireworks show light up the sky from the peaceful waters of
	 Hermann Park\, with a special pedal boat rental from 8:30–10:30 p.m. on S
	aturday\, July 4! 🎇 \nAs we celebrate 250 years of American independence\,
	 gather your crew and watch the sky come alive with fireworks while cruisi
	ng across the lake in your own pedal boat under the stars. 🌟  \nSaturday\,
	 July 4\n8:30 – 10:30 p.m.  \n🎟️ $150 per boat (up to 4 people) includes:\n
	🕘 Boat rental up to 2 hours\n🍿 Drinks & snacks\n🎊 Festive accessories\n🅿️ R
	eserved parking in Lot I near Lake Plaza\n⛵ Board anytime between 8:30–9:3
	0 p.m. and enjoy the show from the water (fireworks begin at approximately
	 9:45 p.m.\, boats must return once fireworks finish) \nBOOK YOUR BOAT HER
	E!  \n🚨 Important Info: \n\nOne rider per boat must be 18+\nAll riders 18+
	 must sign a digital waiver before boarding\nAt least one rider must be 18
	+\, with a physical government ID\, and sign a waiver before boarding\nTic
	kets are non-refundable\nEvent is rain or shine per Miller Outdoor Theatre
	’s plan\nIn the event of lightning\, pedal boats will close\, and refunds 
	will be issued \n\nThe purchase of a ticket includes an up-to 2-hour pedal
	 boat ride for up to 4 people to enjoy the sight of Miller Outdoor Theatre
	’s fireworks show\, drinks\, snacks\, festive treats\, and a reserved park
	ing spot in Lot I near Lott Hall by Lake Plaza (starting at 8 p.m.). Only 
	one ticket purchase of $150 is needed for a 4-person boat (i.e. it is the 
	cost per boat\, not per rider).  \nA reminder that at least one rider per 
	boat must be 18 years or older.  All riders 18 years or older must sign a 
	digital waiver before boarding. Tickets are non-refundable. We are followi
	ng Miller Outdoor Theatre’s plan for their event and fireworks show which 
	is rain or shine. If there is lightning in the area\, we will close the pe
	dal boats and ticket holders will receive a refund.  \nPlease arrive early
	 to allow time to park in Lot I as roads in the Park will be closed by HPD
	 and closures are subject to change based on their purview.  \n\nhttps://h
	ermannpark.org/event/red-white-cruise-2/\n\nFrom Hermann Park Conservancy
URL:https://hermannpark.org/event/red-white-cruise-2/
LOCATION:Lake Plaza
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:hermann-park
CATEGORIES:Hermann Park Conservancy
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
