	 Pay or Google Pay). Will call tickets can be picked up on day of show at 
	the Box Office. Box Office opens 1 hour prior to door times. You will need
	 a valid photo ID and the credit card used for purchase. ADA tickets can b
	e purchased online - you do not need to call the box office to place an or
	der. Look for the logo on the Find Tickets page to view all available acce
	ssible seats. We do have accessible seating but be advised it may sell out
